data.description: *** M A S S I V E  PRICE REDUCTION! NOW *THIS* IS A DEAL! *** What a beauty! This comfortably-sized two story home on San Antonio's north side has everything you're looking for: a shaded and charming front porch, a true entry/foyer, a dedicated dining room, and the list goes on! The spacious & open eat-in kitchen offers copious countertop space (non-porous Corian counters), modern appliances, and tastefully updated 42" cabinetry, plus a walk-in pantry! The family room, adjacent to the open kitchen for easy entertaining, features a beautifully crafted custom built-in for storage & display. Upstairs you'll find a sprawling loft perfect as a second living room, game room, or even as a fantastic open office space! The primary suite has a wonderful walk-in closet and a roomy full bath ensuite complete with separate shower, tub, and double vanities. The secondary bedrooms are generously sized with great closet space. Don't forget to scope out the adorable powder room decor and then head out back to the peaceful backyard! This house is just across the street from the Prue Road trailhead/entrance, too! Schedule your showing today!
